==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pulverate
<hw>Pul"ver*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pulveratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>pulverare</ets> to pulverize. See
<er>Pulverize</er>.]</ety> <def>To beat or reduce to powder or dust; to
pulverize.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pulverine</ent>⟦br⟧
